Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,地球脉动 III
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}字幕翻译：村儿南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们星球上的很多地区仍未被探索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much of our planet still remains unexplored...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这些地区大部分都被水覆盖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..for most of it is covered by water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次水中之旅都能揭开奇妙事物的面纱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every journey below the surface can reveal something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 每年有超过一千种新物种被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than a thousand new species are discovered here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋是地球上80%动物的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ocean is home to 80% of all animal life on Planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今 要在这个多变的世界中生存发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But today, thriving in this varied world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有时需要做出令人惊讶的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sometimes demands the most surprising behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}第二集\N海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,热带浅海\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The shallow seas of the tropics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里看上去如天堂般美好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This may look like a paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但海面之下 是一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but beneath the surface, it is an arena
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不断进行生死搏斗的竞技场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for constant life-and-death struggles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,隐藏在表面现象背后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where not everything is quite as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,掠食性狮子鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A predatory lionfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正在寻找小虾小鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..on the hunt for shrimp and small fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么多地方可供猎物藏身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With so many places for its prey to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子鱼必须耐心下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the lionfish has to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这只虾看起来很诱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This shrimp appears tempting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当狮子鱼靠近时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the lion-fish closes in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它会展开鳍来迷惑猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it fans out its fins to disorientate its prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人变成了猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hunter becomes the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被浅海中最特别的捕食者之一摆了一道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricked by one of the shallow sea's most extraordinary predators...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大斑躄鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..a clown frogfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它头上带着一根鱼竿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On its head, it carries a fishing rod –
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种改良后的背鳍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a modified dorsal fin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,诱饵很容易被误认为是一只虾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}baited with a lure - easily mistaken for a shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但鱼都不上钩时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, when the fish stop biting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就该把鱼竿收起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's time to pack the rod away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,换个地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对于躄鱼来说 这得花不少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, for a frogfish, that takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,躄鱼不会游泳 反而只会走路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rather than swim, frogfish walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它的鳍实际上相当于脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its fins have, in effect, become feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,躄鱼可能看起来不漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It may not look pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但看似长在它身上的珊瑚实际上是一种伪装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what appears to be coral living on its skin is actually camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,每个钓鱼高手都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As every good angler knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,地点非常重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}picking the right spot is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,摇动钓竿发出震动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jigging the rod sends out pressure waves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,从而吸引猎物的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to attract the attention of possible prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这些鳜鱼被吸引住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These dragonets are certainly interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,彻底上钩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hook, line, and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,浅海往往受益于强烈的阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like all shallow seas, the cold waters off the coast of North America,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,北美沿岸的冷水域也不例外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}benefit from the intensity of the sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, that fuels
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为地球上生长最快的生物之一提供了物质基础\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one of the fastest-growing organisms on the planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,巨藻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..giant kelp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高耸的巨藻森林最终可以达到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Towering forests can eventually reach the height
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,12层楼的高度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of a 12-storey building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些森林是幼年角鲨生长的温床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These forests are nurseries for young horn sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳落下时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the sun begins to set,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它们离开白天的庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they leave their daytime shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前往巨藻森林中心寻找食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and set off into the heart of the kelp forest to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这条只有半米长的鲨鱼非常脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barely half a metre long, this little shark is extremely vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这里生活着巨兽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are monsters here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一条巨大的海鲈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A giant sea bass –
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,重达200公斤以上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}weighing over 200kg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以及长着巨大牙齿的狼鳗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and wolf-eels, with big teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能够咬碎小红海胆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that can crush little red sea urchins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但最大的危险来自其他鲨鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the biggest danger comes from other sharks -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,皱唇鲨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}houndsharks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,以及巨大的扁头哈那鲨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and huge broadnose sevengills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在这片森林中 最好是保持低调\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this forest, it pays to keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,扁鲨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An angel shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,巨藻森林中最危险的鲨鱼之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..one of the most deadly sharks in the kelp forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也有着最高明的伪装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and certainly the best camouflaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,扁鲨通常会潜伏数天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An angel shark will lie in wait for days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但这条扁鲨已经吸引了太多的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but this one has already attracted too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不欢迎他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 危险解除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the coast is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但扁鲨是全天候捕猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But angel sharks hunt around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸孔可以吹起沙子以掩藏身体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Openings for breathing, called spiracles, blow out sand that helps cover its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱已经布好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trap is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,贴紧海底是躲避大多数捕食者的好办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Staying close to the seabed is a good way to avoid most predators.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,迅雷不及掩耳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faster than the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,角鲨有一种秘密武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Horn sharks have a secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,锋利的尖刺使它们得以幸免于大多数捕食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sharp spikes keep them very much off the menu for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 这条年轻的角鲨可以安全地捕猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, this young horn shark can hunt in safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最起码暂时安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猛烈的冬季风暴扑向了这片巨藻森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Violent winter storms batter these kelp forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些植物会被连根拔起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The plants can be ripped from the seafloor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,被海浪带向远处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and carried away far out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开阔的海洋是一片广袤无奇的沙漠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The open ocean is a vast, featureless desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是一小片漂浮的海藻也会变得弥足珍贵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even a small piece of drifting kelp can become valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是这群鱼一直在寻找的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just what these fish have been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 不引人注目的产卵处十分稀少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, shelter where eggs can be laid unobtrusively is rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因此要充分利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..so they make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每条雌性产下多达一千颗卵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each female produces up to a thousand eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雄性争先恐后使鱼卵受精\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the males rush in to fertilise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些活动吸引了大青鲨的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this activity attracts the attention of blue sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它们为了寻找食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can travel thousands of miles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以在海中移动数千里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through the ocean in search of food...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这些大青鲨可能已经几周没吃过东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and they may not have eaten for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎走运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems that they're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些鱼并不好抓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But these fish are no easy meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它们可是飞鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are flying fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然而这条大青鲨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blue shark, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是奔着鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are not here for the fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而是奔着鱼子来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..they have come for the caviar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但飞鱼群产下的卵非常多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But flying fish lay so many eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,多到鲨鱼的盛宴几乎不会造成影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the sharks' feasts hardly make an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,几个月后 新一代飞鱼又将在空中"展翅"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, in a few months' time, a new generation will take to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对于在大海中寻找居所的生物来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Floating islands of weed are always attractive to creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,漂浮的水草总是很有吸引力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}looking for shelter out in the big blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然而如今的海洋中 取代水草浮岛的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, in today's ocean, they are being replaced by something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,塑料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每年有1200万吨塑料最终流入海洋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}12 million tons of it end up in the ocean every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最致命的是废弃的渔线渔网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The deadliest kind are discarded fishing lines and nets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,每年 约有50多万只动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each year, it's likely over half a million animals are ensnared
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被这些"幽灵网"困住并死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and killed by these "ghost nets."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但有些动物在学习\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But some animals are learning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如何利用这些塑料筏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how to take advantage of the plastic rafts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,将其作为庇护所 甚至作为家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and use them for shelter, or even as a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这只和拇指指甲差不多大的雄性哥伦布蟹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This male Columbus crab – barely bigger than your thumb nail –
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,漂泊无归\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a castaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它紧紧抓着网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clinging to his net,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能已经在洋流中漂流了数月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he may have been drifting on ocean currents for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如今它已经长大了 需要找个伴侣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, fully grown, he needs to find a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但哪儿找呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不是这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿只有它孤零零一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}alone on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哥伦布蟹并不擅长游泳 因此这只雄蟹走投无路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Columbus crabs are not good swimmers, so this male is marooned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许一只路过的红海龟是个搭便车的好机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps a passing loggerhead turtle could be the chance to hitch a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,成功抵达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可这里还有别的乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's more than one passenger here -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雌哥伦布蟹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a female Columbus crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它们决定不浪费时间熟悉彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They waste no time in getting acquainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而是直接开始交配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and start to mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这对哥伦布蟹很可能会一起度过余生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This pair may well stay together for the rest of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 海龟身上是个完美的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A turtle, after all, makes an excellent home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报 哥伦布蟹会提供甲板清洁服务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In return, the crabs provide an onboard grooming service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在广袤的海洋中寻找伴侣并不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Finding a partner in the vast ocean is not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,科提兹海 黎明之际\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dawn in the Sea of Cortez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蝠鲼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Mobula rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它们聚集于此 很可能是为了进行繁育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gathering here, most likely to breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,蝠鲼跃出海面的原因尚不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No-one is sure why they leap,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但水花飞溅的声音显然吸引来了更多的同胞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the loud splashes certainly seem to attract more rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.32,0:24:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 听到声音的还有其他生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other creatures, however, are also listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.04,0:24:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虎鲸循声而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Orca have heard the splashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这头雌性虎鲸精通蝠鲼狩猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This female specialises in hunting rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.40,0:25:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但今天 它正在传授两头年轻虎鲸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But today, she is teaching two youngsters
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.24,0:25:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,狩猎蝠鲼的细节诀窍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the finer points of Mobula ray hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.24,0:25:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,蝠鲼的速度很快 甚至快于虎鲸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rays are fast and can outmanoeuvre an orca.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:26:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雌虎鲸明白它需要将猎物驱赶到一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She knows she needs to herd the prey into a tight group...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.68,0:26:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但这项工作无法独自完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but she can't do that on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而是需要团队合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will take teamwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.16,0:26:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而这正是这节课的主题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that is today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.16,0:26:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻的虎鲸理解的很快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The young orca are quick to catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.76,0:26:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,蝠鲼群被包围了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rays are surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.84,0:26:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们迅速下潜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They dive...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.00,0:26:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,却被经验丰富的雌虎鲸逼回海面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..only to be forced back up again by the experienced female.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.88,0:26:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,精疲力竭的蝠鲼无路可逃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, with the exhausted rays trapped against the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.28,0:27:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雌虎鲸发动进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.64,0:27:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻虎鲸则紧跟它的脚步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and the young ones follow her lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.60,0:27:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这一家子是已知的虎鲸群中 唯一用这种方式捕猎蝠鲼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This family are the only orca known to hunt rays like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.96,0:27:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而且效率十分之高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and they are lethally efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.80,0:27:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎今天的课程到此为止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it appears that school is over for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.20,0:27:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这些幸存下来的伤痕累累的蝠鲼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a few battle-scarred survivors,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以暂时喘一口气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's a lucky reprieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.88,0:28:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虎鲸离开后 蝠鲼群得以继续它们的求偶行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the orca gone, the rays can resume their courtship...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.04,0:28:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且规模惊人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and they do so in astounding numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.12,0:28:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,数以万计的蝠鲼聚集在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tens of thousands of rays in a single shoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.64,0:28:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋中还有广阔的区域尚未探索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vast areas of our ocean are yet to be explored.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:28:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这之中最不为人知的区域是海洋深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The least known parts of it are its great depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.48,0:29:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只有高度专业化的潜艇才能抵达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only highly-specialised vessels can take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.08,0:29:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,随着越潜越深 阳光会迅速减弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you descend, the sunlight rapidly fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.84,0:29:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,200米深处 是一片黄昏世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}200m down, you enter the twilight zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.80,0:29:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛置身外星 超乎想象的生物生存于此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..an alien world, inhabited by creatures beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.72,0:30:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,管水母 身披一层致命的刺触须\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A siphonophore – with a cloak of lethal stinging tentacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.76,0:30:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,管水母反复地自我复制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Siphonophores repeatedly clone themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.84,0:30:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不断生长 体长极长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so grow to immense lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这一只达到了45米 是有记录以来所有动物中最长的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one measures 45m and is the longest animal ever recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,附近存在着如此致命的捕食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With such deadly predators around,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.32,0:30:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的生物因此不遗余力地隐藏自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}creatures here go to great lengths to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.68,0:31:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,玻璃鱿鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A glass squid...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.84,0:31:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,身体完全透明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..completely transparent,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.64,0:31:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,除了眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}except for its eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.72,0:31:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以及胃部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.00,0:31:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它很难在黑暗中被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it is extremely difficult to find in the gloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.04,0:31:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,1000米深处以下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Below 1,000m,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.92,0:31:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一缕阳光也无法照射进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all traces of sunlight have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.84,0:31:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一片午夜世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the midnight zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在永恒的黑暗中捕捉食物十分困难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catching food in the perpetual darkness is not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.24,0:32:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吞鳗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A gulper eel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.72,0:32:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它巨大且可伸展的嘴部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its giant, extendable mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.92,0:32:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吞下比自身还大的猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can engulf prey larger than its own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.88,0:33:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再往下三公里 终于抵达了洋底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two miles down, you finally reach the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.56,0:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,相比于此 我们对火星表面的了解还更多一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know more about the surface of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.48,0:33:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的水压是海面处的300倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pressure of the water is 300 times greater than at the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.60,0:33:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且十分寒冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and it's freezing cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.36,0:33:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然而令人惊奇的是 依然有动物生活于此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet, amazingly, there are animals living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.72,0:33:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Muusoctopus robustus\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Muusoctopus robustus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,绰号珍珠章鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nicknamed the pearl octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.88,0:34:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样的极端条件下繁殖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Breeding, in these extreme conditions poses
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.56,0:34:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给这种动物带来了一个特殊的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a particular problem for these animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.68,0:34:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在如此低温下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At these low temperatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.00,0:34:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雌性珍珠章鱼卵发育时间长达十数年之久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this female's eggs could take over ten years to develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它会前往一个特别的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So she travels to a very special place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世上已知的最大规模的章鱼聚集群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the largest known gathering of octopus in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.48,0:35:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它与其他两万只雌性珍珠章鱼一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She joins 20,000 other females...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.44,0:35:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这里产卵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..all here to lay their eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.80,0:35:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在地壳深处被加热的水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Water, heated deep in the Earth's crust,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从海底的板块裂缝中涌出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rises through cracks in the seabed...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.56,0:35:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,将温度升高至10摄氏度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..raising the temperature to as much as 10 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.24,0:35:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,形成一片深海温泉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A deep-sea thermal spa!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.08,0:35:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,温暖的水显著加速了珍珠章鱼卵的发育\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This warmth significantly speeds up the development of their eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.28,0:35:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但尽管如此 小章鱼也需要近两年时间才能孵化出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even so, they will still take nearly two years to hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.60,0:35:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦雌性珍珠章鱼安顿下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once a female is settled,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.04,0:35:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,它便再也不会移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she won't move from her spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.08,0:35:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不会进食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..not even to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.12,0:36:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它会一直照顾自己的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She will constantly tend to her brood –
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.20,0:36:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,保持孩子们的清洁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}keeping them clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.12,0:36:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,以及使用水流为孩子供氧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and oxygenating them with jets of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.48,0:36:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,珍珠章鱼母亲是世上最无私奉献的母亲之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pearl octopus mothers must surely be amongst the most devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.88,0:36:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,两年间 这份艰苦的工作对珍珠章鱼母亲的身体造成了严重的损伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After almost two years, the ordeal take its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.36,0:37:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但漫长的坚守也终于进入了尾声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the vigil is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.92,0:38:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,珍珠章鱼母亲温和地鼓励最后一窝孩子走出家门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last of the brood are gently encouraged to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.28,0:38:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这也用尽了它的最后一丝力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this will be a final act.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.08,0:38:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,像每一只珍珠章鱼母亲一样 它已经饥寒交迫 精疲力竭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like all the mothers here, this octopus is starved and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.52,0:38:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它的生命也走到了终点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her life will soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.52,0:38:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样的无私奉献意味着它的后代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this devotion means that her offspring are among
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.16,0:38:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,将是所有章鱼中个头最大 发育最完善的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the largest and most developed of any octopus
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.04,0:39:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,将在严酷的深海世界中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and have the best chance of survival
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.72,0:39:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有最佳的生存机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the demanding world of the deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.92,0:39:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,每年我们都会发现更多这种奇异的热泉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're finding more of these strange hot springs every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在某些地方 热泉的剧烈程度相当惊人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In some places, they can be astonishingly violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.56,0:39:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,足以融化铅的过热水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Super-heated water – hot enough to melt lead -
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.36,0:39:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从海底喷涌而出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spouts from the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.48,0:39:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,溶解的矿物质在热泉周围凝结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dissolved minerals condense around them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.96,0:39:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,形成高耸的烟囱状 被称为深海热液喷口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to form towering chimneys, known as hydrothermal vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.44,0:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,深海热液喷口是独特动物群落的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are home to unique communities of animals
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.24,0:40:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些动物依靠滚烫的水中的营养物质生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that all rely on the nutrients in the scalding water.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.04,0:40:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有观点认为四十亿年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some suggest that vents like these could be the places
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.88,0:40:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,生命正是起源于类似这样的喷口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where life on Earth first began four billion years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如今有证据表明 木星和土星的卫星上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there is now evidence of hydrothermal vents
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.20,0:40:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,同样存在热液喷口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the moons of Jupiter and Saturn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.20,0:40:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也能孕育生命吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could they too be supporting life?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.60,0:40:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在地球上 这些喷口的影响范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here on Earth, the influence of these vents
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.92,0:40:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,远远不止于烟囱周围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}extends far beyond their chimneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.56,0:41:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,烟雾中携带的基本营养物质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The essential nutrients carried in these plumes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以一直上升至三公里之上的海平面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can rise all the way to the surface two miles above.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.32,0:41:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 它们能极大的促进微小海洋植物的生长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, they stimulate the rapid growth of tiny marine plants on an astronomic scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.60,0:41:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大量的浮游植物产生了地球上一半的氧气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This phytoplankton is so abundant that it produces half of all the oxygen on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.40,0:41:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,浮游植物同时也是许多微小动物的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's also food for a host of minute animals -
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.48,0:42:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是浮游动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}zooplankton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,它们共同构成了海洋中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together, they are the basis of the food chains
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.28,0:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎所有生命的食物链基础\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that sustain nearly all life in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.04,0:42:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在南美洲附近的太平洋海域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the Pacific waters off South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.52,0:42:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是聚集在这里的数十亿条凤尾鱼的食物来源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they feed anchovy that gather here in billions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.76,0:42:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上生产力最高的生态系统之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is one of the world's most productive ecosystems.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.80,0:42:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这些南美海狮正在捕猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These South American sea lions are on the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里的凤尾鱼群已经被发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the anchovy shoal has already been located...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.28,0:43:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,被地球上最高效的捕猎者捷足先登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..by the planet's most efficient hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.04,0:43:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一张近1公里长的渔网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A net, over half a mile long,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.80,0:43:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,将鱼群包围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}encircles the shoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它能捕获超过一百万条鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can trap over a million fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.76,0:43:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些海狮是不会空着肚子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the sea lions aren't about to go hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.92,0:44:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它们学会了寻找渔网上的破洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have learnt to look for holes in the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.04,0:44:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这么容易就能填饱肚子 何必还费劲捕猎呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why waste energy when food comes to you as easily as this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.32,0:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,随着越来越多海狮的到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As more and more sea lions arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.60,0:44:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一些海狮改变了策略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some change their tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.68,0:44:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它们排列在渔网两侧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They line up on both sides of the net...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.36,0:44:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后静候佳音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.96,0:45:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,渔网收紧时 凤尾鱼惊慌失措 纷纷跃向水面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the net tightens, the anchovy panic and rush for the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.24,0:45:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,海狮等的就是这个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the moment the sea lions have been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.64,0:45:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种非常高效的狩猎方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's such an effective way of hunting that the sea lions here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.40,0:45:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的海狮正在改变它们天生的习性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are changing their natural behaviour...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.40,0:45:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万的海狮聚集在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and are raiding the fishing nets
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.20,0:45:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,掠夺渔网中的凤尾鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in their thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.32,0:45:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,随着渔网被彻底收紧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the net almost drawn in,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.56,0:46:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,渔民们发出了警告信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fishermen beat out a warning signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.28,0:46:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.68,0:46:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在混乱中 有些海狮没能成功逃脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the confusion, not everyone manages to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.40,0:46:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,被困在渔网中的海狮有被淹死的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trapped sea lions are in danger of being drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.60,0:47:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,幼崽与母亲被迫分离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pups are separated from their mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.12,0:48:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在最后一刻 渔民们短暂的松开了渔网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, at the last minute, the fishermen briefly drop their net...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.24,0:48:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被困海狮得以逃脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and the trapped sea lions can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.64,0:48:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然而幸运获救的只是少数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But many are not so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.76,0:48:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,世界范围内 每天数以百万计的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Around the world, millions of animals are accidently caught
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.80,0:49:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被渔网意外捕获并最终失去生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and die in fishing nets every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.28,0:49:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这种被称为副渔获物的意外捕获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this by-catch, as it's known,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.08,0:49:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,正在将许多物种推向灭绝的深渊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is pushing many species toward extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.32,0:49:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,动物以非凡的进化过程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Animals have evolved in remarkable ways
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.72,0:49:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,逐渐适应了海洋生存环境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the demands of life in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.04,0:49:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然而如今面对新的挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But can they now adapt to the new challenge -
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.32,0:49:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它们能适应如何与人类共存吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}living alongside us?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.32,0:49:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}幕后花絮
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.04,0:49:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,广袤的海洋是地球上一些最大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The open ocean is home to some of the largest
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.16,0:49:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最特别的动物的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and most extraordinary animals on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.32,0:50:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里 加那利群岛附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here, off the Canary Islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.56,0:50:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,「地球脉动」摄制组正在寻找海洋中一种体型较小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Planet Earth team are searching for one of its smaller,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.16,0:50:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不被人熟知的居民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and less familiar residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.80,0:50:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在寻找一种叫哥伦布蟹的小生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking for a tiny creature called a Columbus crab,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.36,0:50:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只有拇指指甲大小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is only about the size of your thumbnail,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.52,0:50:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,生活在海上的漂浮物体上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which live on floating objects in the open ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.20,0:50:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哥伦布蟹曾经只能在天然漂浮物上发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Columbus crabs were once only found on natural debris,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.52,0:50:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,比如浮木或者海藻上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like driftwood or seaweed,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.60,0:50:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但海洋一直在变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the oceans are changing,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.64,0:50:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它们不得不适应新的环境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they've been forced to adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.84,0:50:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,最容易从中找到哥伦布蟹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The best place to find Columbus crabs
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.98,0:50:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是塑料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is in plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.66,0:50:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们见到的漂浮物中有90%都是塑料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because around 90% of the things we see drifting are plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.24,0:50:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,最多见的漂浮物是废弃渔具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the most common items they find is discarded fishing gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.96,0:50:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,每年有超过一百万吨渔具被丢弃到海洋中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over a million tons is left adrift in the ocean each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.80,0:50:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哥伦布蟹如今正以这些人造物品为家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Columbus crabs are now making their homes on these unnatural materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.38,0:51:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿有只蟹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.64,0:51:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊讶的是 哥伦布蟹在这些新家中发展蓬勃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surprisingly, Columbus crabs are thriving on this new habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.20,0:51:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于较大的海洋生物来说 废弃渔网有着致命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, for larger ocean creatures, these nets can be lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.12,0:51:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,红海龟尤其脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loggerhead sea turtles are especially vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.40,0:51:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很多时候它们会因此身受重伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many times, they are very injured
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.80,0:51:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至往往失去生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and many times they don't even survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.68,0:51:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现状很不乐观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a sad situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.64,0:51:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,通常来说 野生纪录片团队只应观察生命的自然习性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As a rule, wildlife film-makers observe natural behaviour
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.64,0:51:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而不应加以干涉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and do not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.36,0:51:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但这已远非自然习性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is far from natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.68,0:51:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制团队认为他们必须采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The team feel they must take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.48,0:52:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来这只海龟情况还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems that the turtle is quite OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.84,0:52:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只需割开塑料 然后释放它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll just finish to cut the plastic and then we release it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.92,0:52:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个苦乐参半的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a bittersweet moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.12,0:52:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄中救出的多达八只海龟 这仅是其中之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as this is one of eight turtles they rescued whilst filming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.36,0:52:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况不是自然的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This situation is not natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.68,0:52:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而是人类造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's something that is being caused by human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.04,0:52:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾的是 摄制组不得不在多个拍摄地点中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadly, the crew now face dilemmas like this
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.48,0:52:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,面对类似的窘境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on many of their filming expeditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.84,0:53:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,包括前往智利太平洋海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..including, when they travelled to the Pacific coast of Chile,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.96,0:53:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拍摄海狮与地球上最大的渔场之一争夺食物的场景时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to show how sea lions are competing for food with one of the biggest fisheries on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.56,0:53:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,队长费尔南多·奥里瓦雷斯带领团队前往捕鱼船队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Expedition leader Fernando Olivares takes the team to the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.52,0:53:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在渔网附近潜水是非常危险的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Diving near fishing nets is extremely dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.16,0:53:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因此潜水团队必须确保得到渔民的全力配合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the crew must ensure they have the full cooperation of the fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.02,0:53:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请求在渔网外部署潜水员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Requesting permission to deploy divers outside the net?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.86,0:53:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,情况允许吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.50,0:53:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,允许 千万小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.75,0:53:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.04,0:54:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在这潜水相当危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pretty hazardous place to dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.12,0:54:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这项工作需要时刻关注潜水员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a case of trying to keep an eye on the divers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.44,0:54:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但海狮也会潜下去呼出泡泡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the sea lions also like to go down and blow bubbles,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.00,0:54:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就有可能会发生你以为你跟着的是潜水员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so you'll think you're following the divers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.84,0:54:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实是海狮的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then a sea lion will pop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.76,0:54:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为了最大限度的确保安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Taking the utmost care,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.88,0:54:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,潜水员仔细观察了这次行动的规模\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the divers get a close-up view of the sheer scale of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.44,0:54:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这张渔网里准有15吨的鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one net must have about 15 tons of fish in it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.00,0:54:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这个小海湾里有八到九艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there's eight or nine boats in this one little bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.12,0:54:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这些只是些小船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and these are just the small boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.80,0:54:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边 有大船在执行更大规模的捕鱼任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out there, there are huge factory ships that are taking even bigger catches.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.28,0:54:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一年能捕到多少鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much fish a year from just here?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.64,0:54:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每年一百万吨上下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From a million tons a year more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.52,0:54:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,捕鱼量如此之大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The catches are so vast,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.16,0:55:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,海狮已经改变了自然习性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the sea lions have changed their natural behaviour
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.28,0:55:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,直接从渔网中捕捉凤尾鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to collect anchovies directly from the nets.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.76,0:55:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但这种方式存在风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's a risky strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.36,0:55:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,船员们多次目睹海狮被渔网捕获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The crew witnessed sea lions caught in nets multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.36,0:55:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太惨烈了 渔网里太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whoa, it's intense mate, there are so many in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.72,0:55:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有一只海狮幼崽困在渔网里 一直在求助母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a pup stuck in the net, calling to its mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.32,0:55:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但母亲除了在渔网的另一侧呼叫也无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and its mother's just on the outside of the net calling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.64,0:55:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很不忍心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's really hard to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.76,0:55:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,海狮幼崽现在很慌张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, the pup's really panicking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.52,0:55:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有时 渔民能够释放困住的海狮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes, fishermen are able to release trapped sea lions...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.36,0:56:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.84,0:56:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,海狮幼崽命在顷刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pup is in serious danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.28,0:56:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制组再次决定采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once again, the crew decide to step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.84,0:56:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 他要进渔网里救那只海狮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, he's going to go inside of the net to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.88,0:56:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice, really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.80,0:56:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这次可以松一口气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a relief this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.40,0:56:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但这也凸显了拍摄野生动物新的实际情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..but it highlights the new realities of filming wildlife
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.88,0:57:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在如今瞬息万变的海洋中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in today's changing ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.56,0:57:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集 茫茫荒野之旅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time, a journey to Earth's greatest wilderness -
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.60,0:57:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前往沙漠与草原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}deserts and grasslands...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.72,0:57:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 大自然上演动人心弦的精彩戏码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..where nature puts on its most dramatic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.04,0:57:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,「栖息地探索者」生动地展现动物和它们的栖息地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Habitat Explorer brings animals and their habitats to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.16,0:57:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,探索这个免费互动程序并制作折纸动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explore this free interactive and make origami animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.80,0:57:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,前往bbc.co.uk/planetearth3\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to bbc.co.uk/planetearth3
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.88,0:57:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,点击链接进入开放大学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And follow the links to the Open University.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.28,0:57:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或者订购免费印刷版\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or to order a free printed version,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.44,0:57:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎访问网站或拨打屏幕上的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}visit the website or call the numbers on the screen.


